{"tid":1248062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"被人叫去做保險.....","createTime":"2019-06-21T10:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T11:38:02.000Z","uid":257864,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"57fac799899b1f42db334357d34d4646f3c49d70","tid":1248062,"uid":257864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:40:04.000Z","msg":"因為小弟啱啱畢業諗住搵工 跟住有個打波既師兄就見我未搵到工 叫我去佢做緊既保險公司（綠色）度聽下講座同埋睇下工作環境...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我上到去之後 佢就係咁介紹佢團隊有幾好，佢大佬有幾巴閉（心諗黑社會咩宜家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />） 話呢個時事好啱做保險搵大陸人錢，又話佢大佬係咩政協委員 淨係係大陸拋呢個名出來就有一大班 大陸佬跪係面前俾錢你使.... <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講真。聽完之後真係心動....個師兄順手幫我報埋考試....我都以為自己真係會去做保險<br />\n<br />\n我呢幾日屎忽痕上網search 下佢大佬個名...<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/龙子明\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E9%BE%99%E5%AD%90%E6%98%8E&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDcoWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=a42af161\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/龙子明</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/opinion/233119/2019/0617/304852.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fopinion%2F233119%2F2019%2F0617%2F304852.html&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDcoWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=f4849deb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/opinion/233119/2019/0617/304852.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140228/18640693\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140228%2F18640693&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDcoWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=da3e211f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140228%2F18640693&h=60725f7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140228/18640693</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20120708/16494455\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120708%2F16494455&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDcoWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=66240fde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120708%2F16494455&h=e789a870\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20120708/16494455</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完d新聞之後.....我直接覆左我個師兄一句....<br />\n道不同不相為謀 跟住收左佢線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52ac93f2a073f869ecdbdff72cea93b95344cbf","tid":1248062,"uid":245126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac18b9588a6631c26cf95e2949dcfcc5edd4e3aa","tid":1248062,"uid":245126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:43:49.000Z","msg":"祝你早日搵到工<br />\n好鍾意你兩隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b97ddc71cdea86f0a1dcd4e9dea028c896c648","tid":1248062,"uid":257864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ac18b9588a6631c26cf95e2949dcfcc5edd4e3aa","tid":1248062,"uid":245126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:43:49.000Z","msg":"祝你早日搵到工<br />\n好鍾意你兩隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i